msgstr "Hur sparar extra betalningar pengar?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:41
msgid ""
"Extra payments go directly to principal, reducing the balance that accrues "
"interest. This means you pay less interest overall and finish your loan "
"faster."
msgstr ""
"Extra betalningar går direkt till kapitalbeloppet, vilket minskar saldot som"
" löper på ränta. Detta innebär att du betalar mindre ränta totalt sett och "
"avslutar ditt lån snabbare."

