#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/anorexic_bmi_calculator.html:381
msgid ""
"Your calculated BMI number. Lower values indicate lower body weight relative"
" to height."
msgstr ""
"Ditt beräknade BMI-tal. Lägre värden indikerar lägre kroppsvikt i "
"förhållande till längd."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/anorexic_bmi_calculator.html:385
msgid "Category & Severity"
msgstr "Kategori & Allvarlighet"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/anorexic_bmi_calculator.html:387
msgid ""
"Shows which BMI range you fall into and the severity level. This helps "
"identify if professional consultation is recommended."
msgstr ""
"Visar vilket BMI-intervall du hamnar i och svårighetsgraden. Detta hjälper "
"till att identifiera om professionell konsultation rekommenderas."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/anorexic_bmi_calculator.html:391
msgid "Healthy Weight Minimum"
msgstr "Hälsosam vikt minimum"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/anorexic_bmi_calculator.html:393
msgid ""
"The minimum weight (at BMI 18.5) considered healthy for your height. This is"
" a target for gradual, supervised weight restoration if needed."
msgstr ""
"Minimivikten (vid BMI 18,5) som anses vara hälsosam för din längd. Detta är "
"ett mål för gradvis, övervakad viktåterställning om det behövs."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/anorexic_bmi_calculator.html:399
msgid ""
"The difference between your current weight and the minimum healthy weight. "
"This is informational only—weight restoration should always be supervised by"
" healthcare professionals."
msgstr ""
"Skillnaden mellan din nuvarande vikt och den lägsta hälsovikten. Detta är "
"endast informativt – viktåterställning bör alltid övervakas av "
"sjukvårdspersonal."

