#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmi_calculator.html:4
msgid "BMI Calculator - Calculate Your Body Mass Index"
msgstr "BMI Calculator - Beräkna ditt Body Mass Index"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmi_calculator.html:5
msgid ""
"Free BMI calculator to calculate your Body Mass Index. Supports both metric "
"and imperial units. Get instant results with category interpretation and "
"healthy weight range."
msgstr ""
"Gratis BMI-kalkylator för att beräkna ditt Body Mass Index. Stöder både "
"metriska och imperialistiska enheter. Få omedelbara resultat med "
"kategoritolkning och hälsosamt viktområde."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmi_calculator.html:24
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/views/index.py:15
#: core/templates/core/index.html:103
msgid "BMI Calculator"
msgstr "BMI-kalkylator"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmi_calculator.html:27
msgid ""
"Calculate your Body Mass Index (BMI) to understand your weight status. BMI "
"is a measure of body fat based on height and weight."
msgstr ""
"Beräkna ditt Body Mass Index (BMI) för att förstå din viktstatus. BMI är ett"
