#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmi_calculator.html:295
msgid ""
"Body Mass Index (BMI) is a measurement of a person's leanness or corpulence "
"based on their height and weight, and is intended to quantify tissue mass. "
"It is widely used as a general indicator of whether a person has a healthy "
"body weight for their height."
msgstr ""
"Body Mass Index (BMI) är ett mått på en persons magerhet eller korpulens "
"baserat på deras längd och vikt, och är avsett att kvantifiera vävnadsmassa."
" Det används ofta som en allmän indikator på om en person har en hälsosam "
"kroppsvikt för sin längd."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmi_calculator.html:298
msgid "BMI = Weight (kg) ÷ Height (m)²"
msgstr "BMI = Vikt (kg) ÷ Höjd (m)²"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmi_calculator.html:301
msgid ""
"These ranges of BMI vary based on factors such as region and age, and are "
"sometimes further divided into subcategories such as severely underweight or"
" very severely obese. Being overweight or underweight can have significant "
"health effects."
msgstr ""
"Dessa intervall av BMI varierar baserat på faktorer som region och ålder, "
"och delas ibland ytterligare in i underkategorier som kraftigt underviktiga "
"eller mycket kraftigt feta. Att vara överviktig eller underviktig kan ha "
"betydande hälsoeffekter."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmi_calculator.html:310
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:323
msgid "Underweight: BMI &lt; 18.5"
msgstr "Undervikt: BMI &lt; 18.5"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmi_calculator.html:312
msgid ""
"This range includes severe thinness (&lt;16), moderate thinness (16-17), and"
" mild thinness (17-18.5). You may need to gain weight. Consult with a "
"healthcare provider."
msgstr ""
"Detta intervall inkluderar svår tunnhet (&lt;16), måttlig tunnhet (16-17) "
"och mild tunnhet (17-18,5). Du kan behöva gå upp i vikt. Rådgör med en "
"vårdgivare."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmi_calculator.html:316
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:329
msgid "Normal Weight: BMI 18.5-24.9"
msgstr "Normalvikt: BMI 18,5-24,9"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmi_calculator.html:318
msgid ""
"Congratulations! You are in a healthy weight range. Continue maintaining a "
"balanced diet and regular physical activity."
msgstr ""
"Grattis! Du ligger inom ett hälsosamt viktområde. Fortsätt att upprätthålla "
"en balanserad kost och regelbunden fysisk aktivitet."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmi_calculator.html:322
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:335
msgid "Overweight: BMI 25-29.9"
msgstr "Övervikt: BMI 25-29,9"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmi_calculator.html:324
msgid ""
"Consider a balanced diet and regular exercise. Small lifestyle changes can "
"help you reach a healthy weight."
msgstr ""
"Consider a balanced diet and regular exercise. Små livsstilsförändringar kan"
" hjälpa dig att nå en hälsosam vikt."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmi_calculator.html:328
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:341
msgid "Obese: BMI ≥ 30"
msgstr "Övervikt: BMI ≥ 30"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmi_calculator.html:330
msgid ""
"This includes Obese Class I (30-35), Class II (35-40), and Class III "
"(&gt;40). Consult with a healthcare provider for a weight management plan."
msgstr ""
"Detta inkluderar överviktiga klass I (30-35), klass II (35-40) och klass III"
" (&gt;40). Rådgör med en vårdgivare för en vikthanteringsplan."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmi_calculator.html:341
msgid "Enter your age and gender"
msgstr "Ange din ålder och kön"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmi_calculator.html:357
msgid ""
"Your calculated BMI number. This value is used to categorize your weight "
"status."
msgstr ""
"Ditt beräknade BMI-tal. Detta värde används för att kategorisera din "
"viktstatus."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmi_calculator.html:363
msgid ""
"The ratio of your measured BMI to the upper limit of normal BMI (25). Values"
" less than 0.74 indicate underweight, 0.74-1.0 is normal, greater than 1.0 "
"is overweight, and greater than 1.2 is obese."
msgstr ""
"Förhållandet mellan ditt uppmätta BMI och den övre gränsen för normalt BMI "
"(25). Värden mindre än 0,74 indikerar undervikt, 0,74-1,0 är normalt, större"
" än 1,0 är övervikt och större än 1,2 är fetma."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmi_calculator.html:369
msgid ""
"Similar to BMI but uses height cubed instead of squared. More reliable for "
"very tall or short individuals."
msgstr ""
"Liknar BMI men använder höjd i kuber istället för kvadrat. Mer pålitlig för "
"mycket långa eller korta individer."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmi_calculator.html:375
msgid ""
"The weight range (BMI 18.5-24.9) considered healthy for your height. This "
"helps you understand your target weight range."
msgstr ""
"Viktintervallet (BMI 18,5-24,9) anses vara hälsosamt för din längd. Detta "
"hjälper dig att förstå ditt målviktsområde."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmi_calculator.html:388
msgid ""
"A circular gauge showing your BMI value visually. The color corresponds to "
"your category (blue for underweight, green for normal, yellow for "
"overweight, red for obese)."
msgstr ""
"En cirkulär mätare som visar ditt BMI-värde visuellt. Färgen motsvarar din "
"kategori (blå för undervikt, grön för normal, gul för övervikt, röd för "
"fetma)."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmi_calculator.html:414
msgid "BMI Formula"
msgstr "BMI formel"

