msgstr "Granska dina BMR, TDEE, kalorimål och makrorekommendationer"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:447
msgid "Use the calorie targets to plan your diet based on your goals"
msgstr "Använd kalorimålen för att planera din kost baserat på dina mål"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:456
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calorie_calculator.html:410
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:465
msgid "BMR (Basal Metabolic Rate)"
msgstr "BMR (Basal Metabolic Rate)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:458
msgid ""
"The number of calories your body burns at rest. This is your baseline "
"calorie requirement for basic bodily functions."
msgstr ""
"Antalet kalorier din kropp förbränner i vila. Detta är ditt "
"baslinjekaloribehov för grundläggande kroppsfunktioner."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:462
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calorie_calculator.html:416
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:471
msgid "TDEE (Total Daily Energy Expenditure)"
msgstr "TDEE (Total Daily Energy Expenditure)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:464
msgid ""
"Your total daily calorie burn including activity. This is the number of "
"calories you need to maintain your current weight."
msgstr ""
"Din totala dagliga kaloriförbränning inklusive aktivitet. Detta är antalet "
"kalorier du behöver för att behålla din nuvarande vikt."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:468
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:287
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:318
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:477
msgid "Calorie Targets"
msgstr "Kalorimål"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:470
msgid ""
"Different calorie goals for weight loss, maintenance, or weight gain. A "
"deficit of 500 calories per day typically results in ~0.5 kg (1 lb) weight "
"loss per week."
msgstr ""
"Olika kalorimål för viktminskning, underhåll eller viktökning. Ett "
"underskott på 500 kalorier per dag leder vanligtvis till en viktminskning på"
" 0,5 kg per vecka."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:476
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Recommended protein, carbohydrate, and fat intake based on your TDEE. "
"Protein is calculated at 1.6g per kg body weight, fat at 25%% of calories, "
"and carbs make up the remainder."
msgstr ""
"Rekommenderat intag av protein, kolhydrater och fett baserat på din TDEE. "
"Protein beräknas till 1,6 g per kg kroppsvikt, fett till 25 %% av kalorierna"
" och kolhydrater utgör resten."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:484
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:414
msgid "Weight Management Tips"
msgstr "Tips för viktkontroll"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:486
msgid "For Weight Loss:"
msgstr "För viktminskning:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:486
msgid ""
"Create a calorie deficit of 500-1000 calories per day. Focus on whole foods,"
" increase protein intake, and combine diet with regular exercise."
msgstr ""
"Skapa ett kaloriunderskott på 500-1000 kalorier per dag. Fokusera på hela "
"livsmedel, öka proteinintaget och kombinera kost med regelbunden träning."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:487
msgid "For Weight Maintenance:"
msgstr "För viktunderhåll:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:487
msgid ""
"Eat at your TDEE level. Monitor your weight weekly and adjust calories as "
"needed based on activity changes."
msgstr ""
"Ät på din TDEE-nivå. Övervaka din vikt varje vecka och justera kalorierna "
"efter behov baserat på aktivitetsförändringar."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:488
msgid "For Weight Gain:"
msgstr "För viktökning:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:488
msgid ""
"Create a calorie surplus of 250-500 calories per day. Focus on nutrient-"
"dense foods and strength training to build muscle rather than fat."
msgstr ""
"Skapa ett kaloriöverskott på 250-500 kalorier per dag. Fokusera på "
"näringstät mat och styrketräning för att bygga muskler snarare än fett."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:500
msgid ""
"BMR calculations are estimates. Individual metabolism can vary based on "
"genetics, muscle mass, hormones, and other factors."
msgstr ""
"BMR-beräkningar är uppskattningar. Individuell ämnesomsättning kan variera "
"beroende på genetik, muskelmassa, hormoner och andra faktorer."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:506
msgid ""
"Activity multipliers are approximations. Your actual calorie burn may differ"
" based on exercise intensity and duration."
msgstr ""
"Aktivitetsmultiplikatorer är approximationer. Din faktiska kaloriförbränning"
" kan skilja sig beroende på träningsintensitet och varaktighet."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:512
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calorie_calculator.html:558
msgid ""
"For best results, track your food intake and weight regularly, and adjust "
"your calorie targets based on your progress."
msgstr ""
"För bästa resultat, spåra ditt matintag och vikt regelbundet och justera "
"dina kalorimål baserat på dina framsteg."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:518
msgid ""
"Consult with a healthcare provider or registered dietitian before making "
"significant dietary changes, especially if you have medical conditions."
msgstr ""
"Rådgör med en vårdgivare eller registrerad dietist innan du gör betydande "
"kostförändringar, särskilt om du har medicinska tillstånd."

