#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_fat_calculator.html:355
msgid "What is Body Fat Percentage?"
msgstr "Vad är kroppsfettprocent?"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_fat_calculator.html:357
msgid ""
"Body fat percentage is the proportion of fat mass to total body weight. "
"Unlike BMI, which only considers weight and height, body fat percentage "
"provides a more accurate assessment of body composition by distinguishing "
"between fat mass and lean mass (muscle, bone, organs, water)."
msgstr ""
"Kroppsfettprocent är andelen fettmassa av total kroppsvikt. Till skillnad "
"från BMI, som bara tar hänsyn till vikt och längd, ger kroppsfettprocenten "
"en mer exakt bedömning av kroppssammansättningen genom att skilja mellan "
"fettmassa och mager massa (muskler, ben, organ, vatten)."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_fat_calculator.html:360
msgid ""
"Knowing your body fat percentage helps you understand your health status "
"better than weight alone, as it accounts for muscle mass and overall body "
"composition."
msgstr ""
"Att känna till din kroppsfettprocent hjälper dig att förstå din hälsostatus "
"bättre än vikten ensam, eftersom det står för muskelmassa och "
"kroppssammansättning."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_fat_calculator.html:366
msgid "US Navy Body Fat Method"
msgstr "US Navy Body Fat Method"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_fat_calculator.html:368
msgid ""
"This calculator uses the US Navy body fat estimation method, which is one of"
" the most accurate measurement-based formulas available. It uses body "
"circumference measurements (neck, waist, and hip for women) along with "
"height to estimate body fat percentage."
msgstr ""
"Denna kalkylator använder US Navy kroppsfettuppskattningsmetoden, som är en "
"av de mest exakta mätningsbaserade formlerna som finns tillgängliga. Den "
"använder kroppsomkretsmått (nacke, midja och höft för kvinnor) tillsammans "
"med längd för att uppskatta kroppsfettprocent."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_fat_calculator.html:371
msgid "For Men:"
msgstr "För män:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_fat_calculator.html:372
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Body Fat %% = 495 / (1.0324 - 0.19077 × log10(waist - neck) + 0.15456 × "
"log10(height)) - 450"
msgstr ""
"Kroppsfett %% = 495 / (1,0324 - 0,19077 × log10(midja - hals) + 0,15456 × "
"log10(höjd)) - 450"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_fat_calculator.html:373
msgid "For Women:"
msgstr "För kvinnor:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_fat_calculator.html:374
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Body Fat %% = 495 / (1.29579 - 0.35004 × log10(waist + hip - neck) + 0.22100"
" × log10(height)) - 450"
msgstr ""
"Kroppsfett %% = 495 / (1,29579 - 0,35004 × log10(midja + höft - hals) + "
"0,22100 × log10(höjd)) - 450"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_fat_calculator.html:377
msgid ""
"All measurements are in centimeters. The formula uses logarithmic "
"calculations to provide accurate estimates based on body circumference "
"measurements."
msgstr ""
"Alla mått är i centimeter. Formeln använder logaritmiska beräkningar för att"
" ge korrekta uppskattningar baserade på kroppsomkretsmätningar."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_fat_calculator.html:386
msgid "Essential Fat"
msgstr "Essentiellt fett"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_fat_calculator.html:388
#, python-format
msgid "Men: 2-5%% | Women: 10-13%%"
msgstr "Män: 2-5 %% | Kvinnor: 10-13 %%"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_fat_calculator.html:391
msgid ""
"The minimum amount of body fat necessary for basic physiological functions. "
"Below this level can be dangerous."
msgstr ""
"Den minsta mängd kroppsfett som krävs för grundläggande fysiologiska "
"funktioner. Under denna nivå kan det vara farligt."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_fat_calculator.html:397
#, python-format
msgid "Men: 6-13%% | Women: 14-20%%"
msgstr "Män: 6-13 %% | Kvinnor: 14-20 %%"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_fat_calculator.html:400
msgid ""
"Very lean body fat levels typical of competitive athletes. Excellent muscle "
"definition."
msgstr ""
"Mycket magra kroppsfettnivåer som är typiska för tävlingsidrottare. Utmärkt "
"muskeldefinition."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_fat_calculator.html:406
#, python-format
msgid "Men: 14-17%% | Women: 21-24%%"
msgstr "Män: 14-17 %% | Kvinnor: 21–24 %%"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_fat_calculator.html:409
msgid ""
"Good body fat level for active individuals. Visible muscle definition, "
"healthy appearance."
msgstr ""
"Bra kroppsfettnivå för aktiva individer. Synlig muskeldefinition, friskt "
"utseende."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_fat_calculator.html:415
#, python-format
msgid "Men: 18-24%% | Women: 25-31%%"
msgstr "Män: 18-24 %% | Kvinnor: 25-31 %%"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_fat_calculator.html:418
msgid ""
"Average body fat level for the general population. May have some excess fat "
"but generally healthy."
msgstr ""
"Genomsnittlig kroppsfettnivå för den allmänna befolkningen. Kan ha lite "
"överflödigt fett men generellt hälsosamt."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_fat_calculator.html:424
#, python-format
msgid "Men: >25%% | Women: >32%%"
msgstr "Män: >25 %% | Kvinnor: >32 %%"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_fat_calculator.html:427
msgid ""
"Excess body fat that may increase health risks. Consider consulting with a "
"healthcare provider."
msgstr ""
"Överskott av kroppsfett som kan öka hälsorisker. Överväg att rådgöra med en "
"vårdgivare."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_fat_calculator.html:438
msgid "Select your gender (affects the formula used)"
msgstr "Välj ditt kön (påverkar formeln som används)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_fat_calculator.html:439
msgid "Enter your age, height, and weight"
msgstr "Ange din ålder, längd och vikt"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_fat_calculator.html:444
msgid "Review charts and body composition analysis"
msgstr "Granska diagram och kroppssammansättningsanalys"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_fat_calculator.html:455
msgid ""
"Measure just below the larynx (Adam's apple) with the tape sloping slightly "
"downward at the front. Keep the tape horizontal and snug but not tight."
msgstr ""
"Mät strax under struphuvudet (Adamsäpple) med tejpen som lutar något nedåt "
"framtill. Håll tejpen horisontell och tät men inte tät."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_fat_calculator.html:461
msgid ""
"Measure at your navel level (belly button), not at the narrowest point. "
"Stand straight, breathe normally, and measure at the end of a normal breath."
" Keep the tape level and parallel to the floor."
msgstr ""
"Mät på navelnivå (navel), inte på den smalaste punkten. Stå rakt, andas "
"normalt och mät i slutet av ett normalt andetag. Håll tejpen jämn och "
"parallell med golvet."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_fat_calculator.html:467
msgid ""
"Measure around the hips at the widest point. This is typically around the "
"buttocks area. Keep the tape measure horizontal and parallel to the floor."
msgstr ""
"Mät runt höfterna på den bredaste punkten. Detta är vanligtvis runt "
"skinkorna. Håll måttbandet horisontellt och parallellt med golvet."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_fat_calculator.html:473
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:388
msgid "Tip:"
msgstr "Dricks:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_fat_calculator.html:473
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:388
msgid ""
"For best accuracy, take measurements in the morning before eating, and "
"measure multiple times to ensure consistency."
msgstr ""
"För bästa noggrannhet, ta mätningar på morgonen innan du äter och mät flera "
"gånger för att säkerställa konsistens."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_fat_calculator.html:485
msgid ""
"Your estimated body fat percentage based on the US Navy formula. This is an "
"estimate and may vary from other measurement methods like DEXA scan or "
"hydrostatic weighing."
msgstr ""
"Din beräknade kroppsfettprocent baserat på US Navy formel. Detta är en "
"uppskattning och kan skilja sig från andra mätmetoder som DEXA-skanning "
"eller hydrostatisk vägning."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_fat_calculator.html:491
msgid ""
"The total weight of fat in your body, calculated as a percentage of your "
"total body weight."
msgstr ""
"Den totala vikten av fett i din kropp, beräknad som en procentandel av din "
"totala kroppsvikt."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_fat_calculator.html:497
msgid ""
"The total weight of everything except fat: muscle, bone, organs, and water. "
"Higher lean mass generally indicates better fitness and health."
msgstr ""
"Den totala vikten av allt utom fett: muskler, ben, organ och vatten. Högre "
"mager massa indikerar generellt bättre kondition och hälsa."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_fat_calculator.html:503
#, python-format
msgid ""
"An estimated weight at which you would have an ideal body fat percentage "
"(10-20%% for men, 18-28%% for women) while maintaining your current lean "
"mass."
msgstr ""
"En uppskattad vikt vid vilken du skulle ha en idealisk kroppsfettprocent "
"(10-20%% för män, 18-28%% för kvinnor) samtidigt som du bibehåller din "
"nuvarande magra massa."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_fat_calculator.html:509
msgid ""
"Your body fat classification based on gender-specific ranges. This helps you"
" understand where you stand relative to health and fitness standards."
msgstr ""
"Din kroppsfettklassificering baserad på könsspecifika intervall. Detta "
"hjälper dig att förstå var du står i förhållande till hälso- och "
"fitnessstandarder."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_fat_calculator.html:523
msgid ""
"This calculator provides ESTIMATES based on body measurements. Actual body "
"fat percentage may vary when measured with more precise methods like DEXA "
"scan, hydrostatic weighing, or BodPod."
msgstr ""
"Denna kalkylator ger UPPSKATTNINGAR baserade på kroppsmått. Faktisk "
"kroppsfettprocent kan variera när den mäts med mer exakta metoder som DEXA-"
"skanning, hydrostatisk vägning eller BodPod."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_fat_calculator.html:529
msgid ""
"Accurate measurements are crucial. Measure at the same time of day, "
"preferably in the morning before eating, and ensure the tape measure is "
"level and snug but not tight."
msgstr ""
"Exakta mätningar är avgörande. Mät vid samma tidpunkt på dagen, helst på "
"morgonen innan du äter, och se till att måttbandet är plant och tätt men "
"inte tätt."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_fat_calculator.html:535
msgid ""
"Body fat percentage is just one indicator of health. Consider other factors "
"like blood pressure, cholesterol, blood sugar, and overall fitness level."
msgstr ""
"Kroppsfettprocent är bara en indikator på hälsa. Tänk på andra faktorer som "
"blodtryck, kolesterol, blodsocker och övergripande konditionsnivå."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_fat_calculator.html:541
msgid ""
"This calculator is for educational and informational purposes only. Always "
"consult with a healthcare provider or registered dietitian for personalized "
"health advice."
msgstr ""
"Denna kalkylator är endast avsedd för utbildnings- och informationssyfte. "
"Rådgör alltid med en vårdgivare eller registrerad dietist för personlig "
"hälsorådgivning."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_fat_calculator.html:548
msgid "Tips for Healthy Body Fat Levels"
msgstr "Tips för hälsosamma kroppsfettnivåer"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_fat_calculator.html:550
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/healthy_weight_calculator.html:374
msgid "Regular Exercise:"
msgstr "Regelbunden träning:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_fat_calculator.html:550
msgid ""
"Combine cardiovascular exercise with strength training to build lean muscle "
"and reduce body fat."
msgstr ""
"Kombinera kardiovaskulär träning med styrketräning för att bygga muskelmassa"
" och minska kroppsfettet."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_fat_calculator.html:551
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/healthy_weight_calculator.html:373
msgid "Balanced Diet:"
msgstr "Balanserad kost:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_fat_calculator.html:551
msgid ""
"Focus on whole foods, adequate protein, and appropriate calorie intake for "
"your goals."
msgstr ""
"Fokusera på hela livsmedel, tillräckligt med protein och lämpligt "
"kaloriintag för dina mål."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_fat_calculator.html:552
msgid "Consistency:"
msgstr "Konsistens:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_fat_calculator.html:552
msgid ""
"Sustainable changes over time are more effective than quick fixes. Aim for "
"gradual progress."
msgstr ""
"Hållbara förändringar över tid är effektivare än snabba lösningar. Sikta på "
"gradvisa framsteg."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_fat_calculator.html:553
msgid "Sleep:"
msgstr "Sova:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_fat_calculator.html:553
msgid "Adequate sleep (7-9 hours) supports metabolism and hormone regulation."
msgstr ""
"Tillräcklig sömn (7-9 timmar) stödjer ämnesomsättningen och "
"hormonregleringen."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_fat_calculator.html:554
msgid "Stress Management:"
msgstr "Stresshantering:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_fat_calculator.html:554
msgid ""
"Chronic stress can affect body composition. Practice stress-reduction "
"techniques."
msgstr ""
"Kronisk stress kan påverka kroppssammansättningen. Öva stressreducerande "
"tekniker."

