#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_surface_area_calculator.html:359
msgid ""
"Each formula may give slightly different results. The Du Bois formula is "
"considered the gold standard, while Mosteller is the simplest to calculate."
msgstr ""
"Varje formel kan ge lite olika resultat. Du Bois-formeln anses vara "
"guldstandarden, medan Mosteller är den enklaste att beräkna."

