msgid ""
"Your total body weight minus all fat. This includes muscles, bones, organs, "
"and water. Higher LBM generally indicates better body composition."
msgstr ""
"Din totala kroppsvikt minus allt fett. Detta inkluderar muskler, ben, organ "
"och vatten. Högre LBM indikerar generellt bättre kroppssammansättning."

