#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:15
msgid "Track your menstrual cycle and predict your next period dates."
msgstr "Spåra din menstruationscykel och förutsäg dina nästa mensdatum."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:24
