#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:375
msgid "What is Protein and Why Do You Need It?"
msgstr "Vad är protein och varför behöver du det?"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:377
msgid ""
"Protein is one of the three macronutrients (along with carbohydrates and "
"fats) essential for human health. It's made up of amino acids, which are the"
" building blocks of muscles, tissues, enzymes, hormones, and many other "
"important molecules in your body."
msgstr ""
"Protein är ett av de tre makronäringsämnena (tillsammans med kolhydrater och"
" fetter) som är avgörande för människors hälsa. Den består av aminosyror, "
"som är byggstenarna i muskler, vävnader, enzymer, hormoner och många andra "
"viktiga molekyler i din kropp."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:380
msgid ""
"Adequate protein intake is crucial for muscle maintenance and growth, immune"
" function, hormone production, and overall health. Your protein needs vary "
"based on your body weight, activity level, age, and fitness goals."
msgstr ""
"Tillräckligt proteinintag är avgörande för muskelupprätthållande och "
"tillväxt, immunfunktion, hormonproduktion och allmän hälsa. Ditt "
"proteinbehov varierar beroende på din kroppsvikt, aktivitetsnivå, ålder och "
"träningsmål."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:386
msgid "Protein Recommendations by Activity Level"
msgstr "Proteinrekommendationer efter aktivitetsnivå"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:389
msgid "Sedentary (0.8 g/kg)"
msgstr "Stillasittande (0,8 g/kg)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:391
msgid ""
"RDA minimum for adults. Suitable for people with little to no exercise. "
"Office work, minimal physical activity."
msgstr ""
"RDA minimum för vuxna. Lämplig för personer med lite eller ingen träning. "
"Kontorsarbete, minimal fysisk aktivitet."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:395
msgid "Light Activity (1.0 g/kg)"
msgstr "Lätt aktivitet (1,0 g/kg)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:397
msgid ""
"Light exercise 1-3 days per week. Walking, light jogging, or recreational "
"activities."
msgstr ""
"Lätt träning 1-3 dagar i veckan. Promenader, lätt jogging eller "
"fritidsaktiviteter."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:401
msgid "Moderate Activity (1.2 g/kg)"
msgstr "Måttlig aktivitet (1,2 g/kg)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:403
msgid ""
"Moderate exercise 3-5 days per week. Regular workouts, sports, or active "
"lifestyle."
msgstr ""
"Måttlig träning 3-5 dagar i veckan. Regelbundna träningspass, sport eller "
"aktiv livsstil."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:407
msgid "Active (1.4 g/kg)"
msgstr "Aktiv (1,4 g/kg)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:409
msgid ""
"Active exercise 6-7 days per week. Intense workouts, competitive sports, or "
"physically demanding job."
msgstr ""
"Aktiv träning 6-7 dagar i veckan. Intensiva träningspass, tävlingsidrotter "
"eller fysiskt krävande jobb."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:413
msgid "Very Active (1.6 g/kg)"
msgstr "Mycket aktiv (1,6 g/kg)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:415
msgid ""
"Very active lifestyle. Physical job, daily intense exercise, or multiple "
"training sessions."
msgstr ""
"Mycket aktiv livsstil. Fysiskt jobb, daglig intensiv träning eller flera "
"träningspass."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:419
msgid "Elite Athlete (1.8 g/kg)"
msgstr "Elitidrottare (1,8 g/kg)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:421
msgid ""
"Elite athlete level. Professional training, multiple daily sessions, "
"competition preparation."
msgstr ""
"Elitidrottare nivå. Professionell träning, flera dagliga pass, "
"tävlingsförberedelser."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:429
msgid "Protein Needs by Fitness Goal"
msgstr "Proteinbehov efter träningsmål"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:432
#, python-format
msgid "Weight Loss (+20%%)"
msgstr "Viktminskning (+20 %)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:434
msgid ""
"Higher protein intake helps preserve muscle mass during calorie deficit and "
"increases satiety, making it easier to stick to your diet."
msgstr ""
"Högre proteinintag hjälper till att bevara muskelmassan under "
"kaloriunderskott och ökar mättnaden, vilket gör det lättare att hålla sig "
"till din kost."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:438
msgid "Maintain Weight (Standard)"
msgstr "Behåll vikt (standard)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:440
msgid ""
"Standard protein intake to maintain current muscle mass and support daily "
"activities and recovery."
msgstr ""
"Standardproteinintag för att bibehålla nuvarande muskelmassa och stödja "
"dagliga aktiviteter och återhämtning."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:444
#, python-format
msgid "Muscle Gain (+10%%)"
msgstr "Muskelökning (+10 %)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:446
msgid ""
"Slightly higher protein intake to support muscle growth and recovery from "
"training. Essential for building new muscle tissue."
msgstr ""
"Något högre proteinintag för att stödja muskeltillväxt och återhämtning från"
" träning. Viktigt för att bygga ny muskelvävnad."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:450
#, python-format
msgid "Cutting (+30%%)"
msgstr "Skärning (+30%%)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:452
msgid ""
"High protein intake to preserve muscle mass during aggressive fat loss "
"phase. Critical for bodybuilders and athletes cutting weight."
msgstr ""
"Högt proteinintag för att bevara muskelmassa under aggressiv fettförlustfas."
" Kritisk för kroppsbyggare och idrottare som minskar i vikt."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:462
msgid "Select your unit system (Metric in kg or Imperial in lbs)"
msgstr "Välj ditt enhetssystem (Mätrisk i kg eller Imperial i lbs)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:463
msgid "Enter your current body weight"
msgstr "Ange din nuvarande kroppsvikt"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:464
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:454
msgid ""
"Select your activity level based on your exercise frequency and intensity"
msgstr ""
"Välj din aktivitetsnivå baserat på din träningsfrekvens och intensitet"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:465
msgid ""
"Choose your fitness goal (weight loss, maintain, muscle gain, or cutting)"
msgstr ""
"Välj ditt träningsmål (viktminskning, underhåll, muskelökning eller "
"skärning)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:466
msgid ""
"Optionally enter your body fat percentage for lean body mass calculation"
msgstr ""
"Ange eventuellt din kroppsfettprocent för beräkning av mager kroppsmassa"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:467
msgid ""
"Click 'Calculate Protein Needs' to see your personalized recommendations"
msgstr ""
"Klicka på \"Beräkna proteinbehov\" för att se dina personliga "
"rekommendationer"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:468
msgid ""
"Review meal distribution, protein sources, and charts to plan your daily "
"intake"
msgstr ""
"Granska måltidsfördelning, proteinkällor och diagram för att planera ditt "
"dagliga intag"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:479
msgid ""
"Your total daily protein requirement in grams. This is calculated based on "
"your body weight, activity level, and fitness goal."
msgstr ""
"Ditt totala dagliga proteinbehov i gram. Detta beräknas utifrån din "
"kroppsvikt, aktivitetsnivå och träningsmål."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:483
msgid "Protein per kg (or lb)"
msgstr "Protein per kg (eller lb)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:485
msgid ""
"The amount of protein per kilogram (or pound) of body weight. This helps you"
" understand the intensity of your protein needs relative to your size."
msgstr ""
"Mängden protein per kilogram (eller pund) kroppsvikt. Detta hjälper dig att "
"förstå intensiteten av ditt proteinbehov i förhållande till din storlek."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:491
msgid ""
"How to distribute your daily protein across meals. Typically spread across "
"4-5 meals for optimal absorption and muscle protein synthesis."
msgstr ""
"Hur du fördelar ditt dagliga protein över måltiderna. Vanligtvis fördelat på"
" 4-5 måltider för optimal absorption och muskelproteinsyntes."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:497
msgid ""
"Common protein-rich foods and how many servings you'd need to meet your "
"daily requirement. Mix different sources for variety and complete amino acid"
" profiles."
msgstr ""
"Vanlig proteinrik mat och hur många portioner du behöver för att möta ditt "
"dagliga behov. Blanda olika källor för variation och kompletta "
"aminosyraprofiler."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:511
msgid ""
"These are general guidelines. Individual protein needs may vary based on "
"age, gender, medical conditions, and specific training programs."
msgstr ""
"Dessa är allmänna riktlinjer. Individuella proteinbehov kan variera beroende"
" på ålder, kön, medicinska tillstånd och specifika träningsprogram."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:517
msgid ""
"Distribute protein intake throughout the day. Aim for 20-40g per meal for "
"optimal muscle protein synthesis."
msgstr ""
"Fördela proteinintaget över dagen. Sikta på 20-40g per måltid för optimal "
"muskelproteinsyntes."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:523
msgid ""
"Include a variety of protein sources. Animal proteins (meat, fish, eggs, "
"dairy) are complete proteins, while plant proteins (legumes, grains) can be "
"combined for complete amino acid profiles."
msgstr ""
"Inkludera en mängd olika proteinkällor. Animaliska proteiner (kött, fisk, "
"ägg, mejeriprodukter) är kompletta proteiner, medan växtproteiner "
"(baljväxter, spannmål) kan kombineras för fullständiga aminosyraprofiler."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:529
msgid ""
"This calculator is for informational purposes only and should not replace "
"professional medical or nutritional advice. Always consult with qualified "
"healthcare providers or registered dietitians for personalized nutrition "
"guidance, especially if you have medical conditions or specific dietary "
"needs."
msgstr ""
"Denna kalkylator är endast avsedd för informationsändamål och bör inte "
"ersätta professionell medicinsk eller näringsrådgivning. Rådgör alltid med "
"kvalificerade vårdgivare eller registrerade dietister för personlig "
"näringsvägledning, särskilt om du har medicinska tillstånd eller specifika "
"kostbehov."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:535
msgid ""
"Very high protein intakes (>2.5 g/kg) may not provide additional benefits "
"and could potentially strain kidneys in individuals with pre-existing kidney"
" conditions. Most people can safely consume 1.6-2.2 g/kg."
msgstr ""
"Mycket högt proteinintag (>2,5 g/kg) kanske inte ger ytterligare fördelar "
"och kan potentiellt belasta njurarna hos individer med redan existerande "
"njursjukdom. De flesta människor kan säkert konsumera 1,6-2,2 g/kg."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:753
msgid "Chicken Breast"
msgstr "Kycklingbröst"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:756
msgid "Greek Yogurt"
msgstr "Grekisk yoghurt"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:757
msgid "Protein Powder"
msgstr "Proteinpulver"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:758
msgid "Lean Beef"
msgstr "Magert nötkött"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:759
msgid "Tofu"
msgstr "Tofu"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:760
msgid "Lentils"
msgstr "Linser"

