#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/target_heart_rate_calculator.html:7
msgid ""
"Calculate your target heart rate zones for different training intensities. "
"Includes Karvonen method and standard formulas."
msgstr ""
"Beräkna dina målpulszoner för olika träningsintensiteter. Inkluderar "
"Karvonens metod och standardformler."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/target_heart_rate_calculator.html:10
msgid ""
