#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/resistor_calculator.html:479
msgid ""
"A resistor is an electrical component that limits or regulates the flow of "
"electrical current. Resistance is measured in ohms (Ω) and is indicated by "
"colored bands on the resistor body."
msgstr ""
"Ett motstånd är en elektrisk komponent som begränsar eller reglerar flödet "
"av elektrisk ström. Resistans mäts i ohm (Ω) och indikeras med färgade band "
"på motståndskroppen."

